---
Transfer playback to a visible device by ID or name

Usage: spotuify transfer [OPTIONS] <DEVICE>

Arguments:
  <DEVICE>  Device ID or exact name

Options:
      --format <FORMAT>  Output format for the mutation receipt [default: table] [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help             Print help
